item.description:
The Demons and Lady Demons are excited to host the biggest Grand Final viewing party in New England this year! Come enjoy the game over some quality brews and meat pies from KO Pies. Cheer on your favorite team (or heckle them, whatever suits your fancy).

$10 at the door gets you admitted and automatic entry into a raffle for some awesome prizes.

We'll see you there!
